Interactive Light Display Project (ILDP):

===== Building =====

ILDP depends on OpenCV.  You must install this to build ILDP.

Basic Steps:
Configure: ./waf configure --prefix=install_prefix
Build: ./waf build
Install: ./waf install

Example:
./waf configure --prefix=/usr/local/lib/python2.5/site-packages --opencv-prefix=/usr
./waf build
./waf install
